data.title: UnbuckleMe® • Kids Car Seat Travel Made Easier
data.meta_description: As Seen on Shark Tank, UnbuckleMe® is a small tool that makes it 50% easier to unbuckle a child’s car seat. For grandparents with arthritis, moms with long nails or kids 4+ who are ready to unbuckle themselves in the school drop-off line.
data.text:
All of our products support proper use of car seats for children. Our Co-Founder is a nationally certified child passenger safety technician (CPST).

All of our accessories are thoughtfully designed, and lightweight to reduce the risk of becoming a projectile in a crash.

We offer a several snack & activity books to keep kids happy in the back seat, to reduce distracted driving from grown ups reaching back.
